OverTone DSP PTH-2A v2.0.0 R2 WiN MacOSX










Inspired by the Pultec EQH equalizers, the PTH-2A provides a cost-effective feature subset of the PTC-2A / EQP-1A emulation. The PTH-2A uses the same filter emulation technology, providing separately adjustable LF Boost and Attenuate controls for the signature Pultec low-end sound, with three selectable frequencies.



Suitable for Windows XP / 7 and Mac OS X Digital Audio Workstations.



System Requirements - Windows PCs:

   32Bit Systems: A PC Running Windows XP / 7 and a VST compatible host application.
   64Bit Systems: A PC Running Windows 7 (64Bit) and a VST compatible host application.

System Requirements - Mac:

   Requires Mac OS X v.10.5.8 - 10.8
   An AudioUnit (cocoa UI) or VST (32 or 64Bit) compatible host.
   Download includes VST for Mac (32 and 64Bit)

Mac versions are now provided as signed packages, for compatibility with Mac OSX Gatekeeper.
